# ── IMPORTANT: DO commit chroma_db/ ─────────────────────────────────────
# The pre-built vector store is committed so Streamlit Cloud doesn't need
# to re-embed on every cold start.  Add it explicitly:
#   git add chroma_db/
# If you want to exclude it (and let the app auto-build on first run):
# chroma_db/
